title: StarsOne v28.10.2017
description: StarsOne program was launched in 2118 with its goal of exploration the nearest stars. Convenient planet was found and process of terraforming was conducting through 7 years. The best volunteers made their way to the cultivated planet in 2125 to plant a colony and establish connection with Earth center.
